FC had the best price so I placed the order at 3pm. Received conformation within 15 minutes. Overnight came another e-mail with a tracking number for ANC. My parcel was on it's way. Much to my delight it arrived at 12.40pm on 12 May, less than 24 hours from ordering! What more could I ask! Big thanks to FC & ANC. I'm very impressed with your service. Overall Rating
